WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.230
Hey, good morning

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:04.670
family! We're excited to be here today.

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:06.990
We're going to do a video together. We

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.470
want to talk about being thankful.

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:12.350
It was just on my heart; the Lord

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:14.749
told me, 'Brandon, part of the

00:00:14.759 --> 00:00:16.070
things that the people are believing for

00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:18.710
manifestation for will come out of being

00:00:18.710 --> 00:00:18.720
thankful.'This

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:20.910
is just where

00:00:20.920 --> 00:00:23.070
we are, and this is what we

00:00:23.080 --> 00:00:25.390
practice: walking in

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:27.710
thanksgiving. I want to get right to

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:29.630
the message.

00:00:29.630 --> 00:00:29.640
We

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:31.189
were just talking, and I was trying to

00:00:31.199 --> 00:00:33.069
make it a casual thing of just what

00:00:33.079 --> 00:00:34.310
we're thinking about. Megan: we're

00:00:34.310 --> 00:00:34.320
believing

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:35.630
for Megan to be healed,

00:00:35.640 --> 00:00:37.590
for the manifestation of her

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:39.990
complete healing.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.750
We see

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:43.510
she's starting to talk a little; words

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:45.470
here and there. Diana's taught her how to

00:00:45.470 --> 00:00:45.480
say—what

00:00:45.480 --> 00:00:47.470
have you been

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:50.470
teaching her? 'In the name of Jesus, I

00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:52.910
am healed.'Yeah, she goes around and

00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:55.310
says that all the time. Megan says that

00:00:55.320 --> 00:00:57.270
now. She goes around the house saying, 'In

00:00:57.280 --> 00:00:58.990
the name of Jesus, I am healed.'And what

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:01.910
was the other thing we work on? 'I have

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:04.549
the mind of Christ.'Yep, and Megan walks around—we

00:01:04.549 --> 00:01:04.559
start,

00:01:04.559 --> 00:01:07.310
and Megan

00:01:07.310 --> 00:01:07.320
finishes—'I

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:10.510
have the mind of

00:01:10.510 --> 00:01:10.520
Christ.'We're

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:12.910
seeing

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:13.950
the

00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:17.950
manifestations of those

00:01:17.960 --> 00:01:21.870
scriptures come to pass in her life. I'm

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:24.350
seeing it in her behavior.

00:01:24.360 --> 00:01:25.950
I thought if we could just get a

00:01:25.960 --> 00:01:28.749
little fraction of the Word inside of

00:01:28.759 --> 00:01:32.550
her, it would change her.

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:33.990
Diana started

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.670
trying to help her, and

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:38.830
it's been amazing to see God just

00:01:38.840 --> 00:01:41.749
take a little bit of scripture.

00:01:41.759 --> 00:01:44.109
She doesn't say the whole thing, but

00:01:44.119 --> 00:01:47.109
'Christ,

00:01:47.109 --> 00:01:47.119
Christ.'That's

00:01:47.119 --> 00:01:48.350
how she started, just

00:01:48.360 --> 00:01:50.950
saying 'Christ, Christ.'Then I was

00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:53.910
adding a word every time and I worked

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:57.350
with it over weeks and months.

00:01:57.360 --> 00:02:00.389
She's finally got it down now. But

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:05.670
she got that down back: 'Christ,

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:12.390
mind, Christ.'It's amazing;

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:16.550
mind, Christ, mind, Christ.

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:18.229
It's

00:02:18.239 --> 00:02:21.949
prayer coming into fruition. It's

00:02:21.959 --> 00:02:24.750
amazing because, like I said, a lot of

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:27.270
people, if you don't see your miracle

00:02:27.280 --> 00:02:29.910
manifest instantaneously, it's not a

00:02:29.920 --> 00:02:33.150
miracle for you. 'Well, God didn't hear

00:02:33.150 --> 00:02:33.160
me.'But

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:35.190
sometimes miracles are

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:37.830
gradual. Regardless of whether it's gradual and

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:40.869
it takes years, or if it takes days,

00:02:40.879 --> 00:02:44.470
it's still a miracle.

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:47.470
God is faithful, so you can't give up

00:02:47.480 --> 00:02:49.030
hope.

00:02:49.040 --> 00:02:51.750
Sometimes it takes a

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:54.070
process. I believe with all my heart

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:57.229
she's healed now, manifestation now, but

00:02:57.239 --> 00:02:58.990
we're walking it out.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:00.390
We're

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:02.750
not giving up hope.

00:03:02.750 --> 00:03:02.760
I

00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:05.350
just wanted to encourage you all that even in

00:03:05.360 --> 00:03:07.990
our life, you might think, 'These

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:10.149
people have their stuff all together and

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:11.949
they're spiritually so strong.'We're

00:03:11.949 --> 00:03:11.959
a

00:03:11.959 --> 00:03:14.190
work in

00:03:14.200 --> 00:03:17.070
progress just like you all. We

00:03:17.070 --> 00:03:17.080
have

00:03:17.080 --> 00:03:21.030
a special needs child,

00:03:21.040 --> 00:03:24.149
and she's been

00:03:24.149 --> 00:03:24.159
potty

00:03:24.159 --> 00:03:26.949
trained now—we're grateful—and the

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:30.229
Lord is working a miracle in her.

00:03:30.239 --> 00:03:32.030
It's been a process. I

00:03:32.040 --> 00:03:33.030
believe in God she's going to wake up

00:03:33.040 --> 00:03:34.190
tomorrow and she's going to talk

00:03:34.200 --> 00:03:35.589
in full sentences, come on here

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:36.949
and tell you all her

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:39.750
testimony. But right now we're taking

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:41.630
baby steps. We're

00:03:41.640 --> 00:03:44.710
excited. We have the mind

00:03:44.720 --> 00:03:47.470
of Christ.

00:03:47.470 --> 00:03:47.480
Diana's

00:03:47.480 --> 00:03:49.869
more working

00:03:49.869 --> 00:03:49.879
in it,

00:03:49.879 --> 00:03:51.110
and so we just want to encourage you

00:03:51.110 --> 00:03:51.120
all

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:53.429
today with that miracle.

00:03:53.439 --> 00:03:55.229
Because where she was, folks—I'm telling

00:03:55.229 --> 00:03:55.239
you—they

00:03:55.239 --> 00:03:57.069
said she would never talk,

00:03:57.079 --> 00:03:58.990
she would never have a normal life;

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:01.990
they gave up on her. Every

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:04.869
little thing we rejoice on; we

00:04:04.879 --> 00:04:06.949
give God all the glory and all the praise.

00:04:06.959 --> 00:04:09.710
It's the biggest deal,

00:04:09.720 --> 00:04:12.470
even small, tiny things, because that's

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:14.830
how you get to the big things: a bunch

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:17.830
of little baby steps makes big

00:04:17.840 --> 00:04:20.150
progress. And being thankful for the

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:22.790
small things—don't just go,

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:24.749
'Whatever, it's just a small

00:04:24.749 --> 00:04:24.759
thing.'Like

00:04:24.759 --> 00:04:26.550
one time I was riding with somebody and

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:29.350
the lady at the

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:30.390
cash

00:04:30.390 --> 00:04:30.400
register

00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:33.469
handed them a free cup of coffee. I

00:04:33.479 --> 00:04:35.510
went, 'Praise God, you just got blessed

00:04:35.520 --> 00:04:38.390
with a free cup of coffee!'And the person

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:40.749
said to me, 'Oh, I don't sweat the small

00:04:40.759 --> 00:04:42.870
things.'I

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:46.469
went, 'Hold on a minute. If you don't

00:04:46.479 --> 00:04:49.110
rejoice over the small things, you won't

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:51.150
rejoice over the big things

00:04:51.150 --> 00:04:51.160
either.'You've

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:53.070
got to grasp a hold of even

00:04:53.080 --> 00:04:56.270
a small cup of coffee. You've got to get

00:04:56.280 --> 00:04:59.430
excited when God blesses you with

00:04:59.430 --> 00:04:59.440
five

00:04:59.440 --> 00:05:01.710
cents.

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:03.790
You can't say, 'I'll be

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:05.550
excited when I get a million

00:05:05.550 --> 00:05:05.560
dollars.'If

00:05:05.560 --> 00:05:08.670
you can't get excited

00:05:08.680 --> 00:05:11.629
over the dollar—come on, folks—we've got

00:05:11.639 --> 00:05:13.909
to be grateful for everything. And that's

00:05:13.919 --> 00:05:16.070
what I'm trying to get across:

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:23.309
it's being grateful. I have to go

00:05:23.319 --> 00:05:24.870
back to even when I was telling

00:05:24.870 --> 00:05:24.880
you

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:26.230
I'm believing for a house, believing for

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:28.189
this, believing

00:05:28.189 --> 00:05:28.199
for that—being

00:05:28.199 --> 00:05:30.189
thankful for what He's already given

00:05:30.199 --> 00:05:32.790
you.

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:34.469
There are times I murmur and complain in my

00:05:34.479 --> 00:05:37.309
heart and I get upset about things;

00:05:37.319 --> 00:05:39.710
you murmur and complain, you whine

00:05:39.720 --> 00:05:41.029
about

00:05:41.039 --> 00:05:44.629
it, and I have to stop.

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:47.029
'Father, just thank You. Thank You that

00:05:47.039 --> 00:05:49.870
today we had a meal. Thank You,

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:53.189
Father, that You provided lights

00:05:53.199 --> 00:05:55.309
for my home. Thank You, Lord, that I have a

00:05:55.319 --> 00:05:57.309
YouTube channel. Thank You, Father, that

00:05:57.319 --> 00:05:58.870
these people even come on here and even

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:01.189
want to listen to

00:06:01.189 --> 00:06:01.199
me.'It's

00:06:01.199 --> 00:06:03.990
humbling. 'Lord, thank

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:06.070
You for all the kind words they give me.

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:08.150
I know, Lord, it's not me, it's all You,

00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:10.790
and I give You all the glory for

00:06:10.790 --> 00:06:10.800
it.'But

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:13.510
they tune in, and I'm

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:15.550
thankful for every single one of them.

00:06:15.560 --> 00:06:18.070
It's very interesting just taking

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:19.790
and being grateful for the small things.

00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:21.830
You may

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:23.110
think, 'I don't have anything to be

00:06:23.120 --> 00:06:25.629
grateful for,'but you say, 'I'm thankful

00:06:25.639 --> 00:06:28.550
for the air that I breathe. I'm thankful

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:29.990
for

00:06:29.990 --> 00:06:30.000
my

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:31.670
sight. I'm thankful I

00:06:31.670 --> 00:06:31.680
have

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:34.070
ears.'Find

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:38.070
something in your life today

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:41.589
to give God praise for. Be grateful

00:06:41.599 --> 00:06:44.230
that you have life,

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:45.870
the opportunity that you woke up

00:06:45.880 --> 00:06:49.189
this morning to breathe.

00:06:49.199 --> 00:06:51.670
You may be in pain, but

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:53.469
something might not hurt. Maybe your toe

00:06:53.469 --> 00:06:53.479
doesn't

00:06:53.479 --> 00:06:55.830
hurt.

00:06:55.840 --> 00:06:57.670
'Thank

00:06:57.680 --> 00:07:00.230
You, Father, my toe

00:07:00.230 --> 00:07:00.240
doesn't

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:04.270
hurt. It could be cut off. Thank

00:07:04.280 --> 00:07:05.710
You, I have a

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:09.189
toe. Thank You, I have an earlobe. Thank

00:07:09.199 --> 00:07:11.029
You, Father, I have an

00:07:11.029 --> 00:07:11.039
eyebrow.'Find

00:07:11.039 --> 00:07:14.510
something to give Him

00:07:14.520 --> 00:07:17.950
praise for today regardless of how bad

00:07:17.960 --> 00:07:21.070
you think you've got it.

00:07:21.070 --> 00:07:21.080
It

00:07:21.080 --> 00:07:24.070
doesn't

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:26.670
matter how small

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:31.029
you think it is; it's big to God.

00:07:31.039 --> 00:07:33.629
God's a good God and He deserves all our

00:07:33.639 --> 00:07:36.189
praise.

00:07:36.199 --> 00:07:39.909
Even if it's for a star

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:42.629
you find in the sky: 'God, I thank You for

00:07:42.639 --> 00:07:45.350
that star right there. Thank You, Father,

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:47.469
for that star. I thank You for the tires

00:07:47.479 --> 00:07:50.189
on my car. I thank You for the dirt I

00:07:50.199 --> 00:07:52.430
walked on today.'If you don't have

00:07:52.430 --> 00:07:52.440
anything

00:07:52.440 --> 00:07:53.710
else to be thankful for, thank

00:07:53.720 --> 00:07:56.390
Him for something. Amen.

00:07:58.840 --> 00:08:01.070
When you start doing

00:08:01.080 --> 00:08:03.110
that, you'll start seeing miracles

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:05.189
manifest in your life. You'll start

00:08:05.199 --> 00:08:07.550
seeing outpourings of the Spirit of

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:09.909
God. God's looking for a

00:08:09.919 --> 00:08:12.070
heart who's perfect towards Him,

00:08:12.080 --> 00:08:14.550
and that is a grateful heart, a cheerful heart,

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:16.350
a heart that's full of joy and

00:08:16.360 --> 00:08:18.230
thankfulness. It

00:08:18.230 --> 00:08:18.240
isn't

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:20.469
easy to do it all the time.

00:08:20.479 --> 00:08:23.110
I have to

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:25.670
catch myself and go back;

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:27.270
I get in my prayer

00:08:27.280 --> 00:08:29.749
time and I go, 'Oh God, I'm

00:08:29.759 --> 00:08:32.709
sorry. I've been fussy today, had a bad

00:08:32.719 --> 00:08:34.990
attitude today. I shouldn't have been

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:37.110
so ungrateful for what You

00:08:37.110 --> 00:08:37.120
have.'He'll

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:40.230
tell me, 'Brandon, really, what's

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:41.469
your problem?'I'll

00:08:41.469 --> 00:08:41.479
say,

00:08:41.479 --> 00:08:44.630
'Well, I'm irritated about this

00:08:44.640 --> 00:08:47.990
and this.'He says, 'But

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:50.750
I've given you so much. I've

00:08:50.750 --> 00:08:50.760
blessed you

00:08:50.760 --> 00:08:52.949
so much. Why can't you take time to thank

00:08:52.949 --> 00:08:52.959
Me for that?'When

00:08:52.959 --> 00:08:55.030
the Lord asks

00:08:55.030 --> 00:08:55.040
you that...

00:08:55.040 --> 00:08:58.670
'God, forgive me. Forgive

00:08:58.680 --> 00:08:59.990
me,

00:08:59.990 --> 00:09:00.000
Lord.'You

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:01.910
want to crawl underneath a rock.

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:09.550
We all have our issues. But I'm just

00:09:09.560 --> 00:09:11.030
trying to tell y'all something that we

00:09:11.040 --> 00:09:13.230
have to do with Megan, and we're thanking

00:09:13.230 --> 00:09:13.240
Him

00:09:13.240 --> 00:09:14.630
for this.

00:09:14.640 --> 00:09:16.470
It's a big deal

00:09:16.480 --> 00:09:19.230
to us. You understand what

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:21.310
I'm saying? You live

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:24.230
it with me. Yeah, you're stirring me up.

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:28.110
It's so good.

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:30.389
It's time to be more thankful.

00:09:33.040 --> 00:09:36.829
I feel His

00:09:36.839 --> 00:09:38.870
presence. Thank You,

00:09:38.880 --> 00:09:51.949
Lord.

00:09:51.959 --> 00:09:54.350
I don't want to just always come on

00:09:54.360 --> 00:09:56.949
here and preach to y'all; I just want to

00:09:56.959 --> 00:10:00.030
tell y'all—just being

00:10:00.040 --> 00:10:01.509
real—just

00:10:01.519 --> 00:10:04.829
being grateful will do a lot in

00:10:04.839 --> 00:10:08.110
your life. I know it seems like some

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:10.710
days are really hard, but

00:10:10.720 --> 00:10:13.910
what I'm telling you right now

00:10:13.920 --> 00:10:17.829
works, for He inhabits the praise of His

00:10:17.839 --> 00:10:21.750
people, and when praises go up, blessings

00:10:21.760 --> 00:10:25.310
come down. If you take your eyes off of

00:10:25.320 --> 00:10:27.310
yourself... I even heard this when I

00:10:27.310 --> 00:10:27.320
traveled

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:30.790
with Benny

00:10:30.790 --> 00:10:30.800
Hinn.

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:32.630
When we'd go in the back room and we'd pray

00:10:32.640 --> 00:10:34.870
for the people in the back—if they took

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:37.389
their eyes off of begging God...

00:10:37.399 --> 00:10:38.829
if you're begging, you're not believing.

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:41.750
If you're begging God for your miracle,

00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:42.790
you're not

00:10:42.800 --> 00:10:45.269
believing. When you take your eyes

00:10:45.279 --> 00:10:46.829
off of yourself and you start praying

00:10:46.839 --> 00:10:49.190
for somebody else, that is usually when the

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:50.550
manifestations start coming

00:10:50.550 --> 00:10:50.560
quickly.

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:51.910
When you're consumed with

00:10:51.920 --> 00:10:53.910
yourself,

00:10:53.920 --> 00:10:55.470
worried about 'I'm

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:57.110
dying, stage four cancer, I only have a couple of days to live, I've got

00:10:59.160 --> 00:11:00.509
to have a

00:11:00.519 --> 00:11:02.430
miracle right

00:11:02.430 --> 00:11:02.440
now,'He

00:11:02.440 --> 00:11:05.269
knows what you need. But when they took

00:11:05.279 --> 00:11:07.629
their focus off of

00:11:07.639 --> 00:11:10.670
their need and started focusing on

00:11:10.680 --> 00:11:13.230
praying for other people's needs, their

00:11:13.240 --> 00:11:16.110
manifestation instantaneously

00:11:19.269 --> 00:11:19.279
came.

00:11:23.519 --> 00:11:25.710
Those

00:11:25.720 --> 00:11:28.550
miracles were real. When I

00:11:28.560 --> 00:11:32.030
ushered,

00:11:32.040 --> 00:11:33.910
I'm telling you, the manifestations

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:36.430
of the glory of God... I've never felt them

00:11:36.440 --> 00:11:38.389
in a meeting like I did whenever I was

00:11:38.399 --> 00:11:39.430
with Benny

